## 4. QUALITY ASSURANCE

### 4.1 Content Quality Standards

#### Accuracy and Completeness
- All content must be factually accurate and up-to-date
- Content must be complete and cover all necessary topics
- Sources must be credible and properly cited
- Content must be reviewed by subject matter experts

#### Clarity and Usability
- Content must be clear and easy to understand
- Language must be appropriate for target audience
- Content must be well-organized and structured
- Navigation must be intuitive and user-friendly

#### Brand Consistency
- Content must align with brand voice and tone
- Visual elements must follow brand guidelines
- Content must reflect company values and mission
- Quality must meet professional standards

### 4.2 Platform Quality Standards

#### Performance
- Page load times must be under 2 seconds
- System uptime must be 99.9% or higher
- Response times must be under 1 second
- Error rates must be under 0.1%

#### Security
- All data must be encrypted in transit and at rest
- Access controls must be properly implemented
- Security vulnerabilities must be patched promptly
- Regular security audits must be conducted

#### Usability
- Interface must be intuitive and user-friendly
- Features must work as expected
- Help documentation must be comprehensive
- User feedback must be incorporated

### 4.3 Service Quality Standards

#### Response Times
- Email support: 24 hours or less
- Phone support: 4 hours or less
- Live chat: 2 hours or less
- Critical issues: 1 hour or less

#### Resolution Rates
- First contact resolution: 80% or higher
- Overall resolution rate: 95% or higher
- Customer satisfaction: 4.5/5 or higher
- Net Promoter Score: 70 or higher

